Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:59.41,Título do Episódio,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fsp1.2\bord0\shad0\c&HFAFFFA&\fs40\pos(636.5,315)}A Bruxa das Trevas e o Fio Vermelho 2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:35.01,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Comecei a ler as recordações\N da Prof. Melusine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.56,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}de há 49 anos atrás, quando foi\N para o mundo dos humanos{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:44.89,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}juntamente com as suas amigas,\N Gyubad e Tika.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:48.39,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Têm de acabar o treino e regressar{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.15,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}antes da areia acabar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:55.99,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}E parece que estão prestes\N a amaldiçoar o Izou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.43,Normal,,0,0,0,,Restam 47 minutos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:03.16,Normal,,0,0,0,,Como vai isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.08,Normal,,0,0,0,,Temos de nos despachar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:06.20,Normal,,0,0,0,,Como o amaldiçoamos?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:08.84,Normal,,0,0,0,,Têm aqui doces \Nque controlam o tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:10.59,Normal,,0,0,0,,Doces que controlam o tempo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.13,Normal,,0,0,0,,O azul avança no tempo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:17.43,Normal,,0,0,0,,o vermelho é para voltar atrás
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:19.68,Normal,,0,0,0,,e o amarelo para o tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:25.27,Normal,,0,0,0,,Se lamberem um dos doces, \Npoderão controlar o tempo como quiserem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:26.82,Normal,,0,0,0,,Estou a ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:29.23,Normal,,0,0,0,,Gyubad, dás-me o doce azul?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:30.61,Normal,,0,0,0,,O que vais fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.30,Normal,,0,0,0,,Já vais ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:33.56,Normal,,0,0,0,,É um feitiço de seca.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.95,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruki-uge, Ruki-uge, Sciamare!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:43.61,Normal,,0,0,0,,A estação das chuvas já terminou?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:45.54,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que Sol tão agradável.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:47.91,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que maldição vem a ser essa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:49.46,Normal,,0,0,0,,Calma, agora vou usar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:51.54,Normal,,0,0,0,,este doce que avança no tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.76,Normal,,0,0,0,,Estamos a avançar no tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.44,Normal,,0,0,0,,Ele terá problemas \Nse não chover, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:16.00,Normal,,0,0,0,,Vamos, fica chateado com o tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:18.91,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que tal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:21.12,Normal,,0,0,0,,Já estás zangado?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.47,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:29.08,Normal,,0,0,0,,Com todo este Sol,\N vou colher batatas-doces deliciosas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.41,Normal,,0,0,0,,Ele está mais animado que chateado.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.50,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não acredito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.46,Normal,,0,0,0,,Bom trabalho, Sol!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.99,Normal,,0,0,0,,Tika, não te rias!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.26,Normal,,0,0,0,,Desculpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.43,Normal,,0,0,0,,Bem, é a minha vez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.64,Normal,,0,0,0,,Vou voltar atrás no tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.98,Normal,,0,0,0,,O que planeias fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:49.27,Normal,,0,0,0,,Primeiro,\N voltemos à estação das chuvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:57.61,Normal,,0,0,0,,Raios! Achei que fosse\N saber a morangos,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.40,Normal,,0,0,0,,mas sabe a gengibre vermelho.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:11.58,Normal,,0,0,0,,O Izou trabalha de manhã à noite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.25,Normal,,0,0,0,,Ele não faz pausas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:17.13,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que vais fazer agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.94,Normal,,0,0,0,,Se a seca não funcionou,\N tentaremos o contrário.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:20.91,Normal,,0,0,0,,Observa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:22.43,Normal,,0,0,0,,o meu feitiço da chuva!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.35,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruki-uge, Ruki-uge, Piovere!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:38.73,Normal,,0,0,0,,Vou fazer com que se chateie \Npor não ter Sol para as batatas-doces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.26,Normal,,0,0,0,,Está a chover a potes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que bom que há chuva!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:47.65,Normal,,0,0,0,,Assim o solo fica mais fofo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:52.03,Normal,,0,0,0,,Será mais fácil de arrancar\N as batatas-doces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:55.08,Normal,,0,0,0,,Cai chuva, cai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.84,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu quero é chuva!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:57.84,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que raio se passa com ele?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:04.59,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Será que o Izou é uma pessoa \Nque não odeia nada neste mundo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.59,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Cai chuva, cai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.46,Normal,,0,0,0,,Têm 20 minutos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.06,Normal,,0,0,0,,Têm de se despachar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.15,Normal,,0,0,0,,Que fazemos?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:14.07,Normal,,0,0,0,,Lançamos-lhe o feitiço\N de morte horrenda?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:15.32,Normal,,0,0,0,,Nem pensar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.19,Normal,,0,0,0,,Porque estás a gritar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.68,Normal,,0,0,0,,Bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:22.61,Normal,,0,0,0,,Se o matarmos, \No nosso treino ficará incompleto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.44,Normal,,0,0,0,,Então pensa nalguma solução.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.57,Normal,,0,0,0,,Estou a tentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:30.80,Normal,,0,0,0,,Isto é incrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.13,Normal,,0,0,0,,É uma flor da batata-doce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:36.79,Normal,,0,0,0,,É raro vê-las desabrochar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:41.55,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ele fica contente \Npor ver flores a desabrochar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.77,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aquela flor lembra-me algo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:47.93,Normal,,0,0,0,,Uma mandragora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.90,Normal,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.95,Normal,,0,0,0,,Parece-se com a mandragora\N do submundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:57.59,Normal,,0,0,0,,Mandragora? A flor que enche\N o teu coração de medo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.36,Normal,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.83,Normal,,0,0,0,,E como o vamos amaldiçoar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.65,Normal,,0,0,0,,Se fizermos desabrochar magicamente\N algumas mandragoras,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:08.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,quando olhar para elas\N ficará cheio de medo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:12.91,Normal,,0,0,0,,e ficará a odiar o mundo.\N Que vos parece?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.69,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não esperava menos da aluna de mérito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:16.96,Normal,,0,0,0,,Muito eficaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:22.71,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mas é uma ideia um tanto cruel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.67,Normal,,0,0,0,,Tika, faz desabrochar \Nalgumas mandragoras.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.56,Normal,,0,0,0,,Vamos terminar isto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.68,Normal,,0,0,0,,Está bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.52,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Este é um passo importante na vida\N de uma bruxa das trevas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:33.38,Normal,,0,0,0,,Lamento, Izou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:41.35,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruki-uge, Ruki-uge, Mandra Fiore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.16,Normal,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.08,Normal,,0,0,0,,Serão flores de batatas-doces?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.08,Normal,,0,0,0,,Conseguiste, Tika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.97,Normal,,0,0,0,,Agora vai ficar cheio de medo\N e partirá em breve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.55,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não temos muito tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.67,Normal,,0,0,0,,Vamos regressar ao submundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.63,Normal,,0,0,0,,São lindas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:11.89,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não cheires o pólen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.99,Normal,,0,0,0,,Tika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.99,Normal,,0,0,0,,As mandragoras são venenosas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:20.69,Normal,,0,0,0,,Se te aproximares delas,\N morrerás, Izou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.73,Normal,,0,0,0,,O doce amarelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:33.78,Normal,,0,0,0,,Mas quando parar de mastigar o doce,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:37.56,Normal,,0,0,0,,o Izou continuará a mover-se\N em direção às flores.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:38.50,Normal,,0,0,0,,Não podemos deixar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.38,Normal,,0,0,0,,Tika, o que é que...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.70,Normal,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruki-uge, Ruki-uge, Amo Mirare!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.44,Normal,,0,0,0,,O fio vermelho do destino?
